answering the "personals," please mail them with your name and address to: P.O. 
Box 644, Livingston, N.J. 07039. Submission of material indicates permission 
for use in publication; name will be kept confidential. 
</P>
<P>
 EILEEN A. KOHUTIS, Ph.D. 
