<P>
 I am working on a biography of Norman Clyde (1885-1972), nature writer and 
mountaineer who made numerous first ascents in the Sierra Nevada and elsewhere. 
I am interested in hearing from anyone who has firsthand knowledge of Clyde, 
and who is willing to share their stories (as well as photos and letters, if 
possible) with me. 
</P>
