<P>
MY BEST SHOT, TOO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Your "My Best Shot" of the entrance to Fowey harbor in Cornwall (Aug. 7) was 
deja vu all over again! Several weeks ago I took exactly the same shot. 
Incidentally, the town of Fowey (pronounced Foy) boasts a couple of illustrious 
literary former residents: Daphne du Maurier and Sir Arthur Quiller-Couch 
(remembered fondly by Helene Hanff in "Q's Legacy"). 
</P>
<P>
 Thanks for the memories. 
</P>
<P>
 DAVID A. BENTLEY 
</P>
<P>
 Los Osos 
