player over 240 pounds (Weir), and seven players are going both ways--Crenshaw, 
Chatman, Weir, Reeves, Taylor, Herzog and Morin. A couple of injuries could 
really wreak havoc. However, if a team is going to be small in size and numbers 
and still contend for the league title, this is the league to do it in. 
