A 'WHACKO' SOCIETY LEGALIZES VIOLENCE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * I can understand your disturbance over the "whackos" who killed two abortion 
providers and a guard ("An Anxious Time for Family Planning," Aug. 25).  
</P>
<P>
 What I consider incommensurately more "whacko" however, is a society that 
legalizes the murder by dismemberment and poisoning of its most innocent 
children -- the unborn -- by the millions, and then has the gall to complain of 
a rise in violence. 
</P>
<P>
 MARTIN WEISS 
</P>
