<P>
40 MEN ARRESTED IN SEX SOLICITATION STING OPERATION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Forty men were arrested after soliciting undercover female police officers for 
sex in a prostitution sting on Harbor Boulevard between Gisler Avenue and 
MacArthur Boulevard, police said. 
</P>
<P>
 The area was targeted Thursday night after complaints from local merchants and 
residents, police said. The sting, which lasted from 7 p.m. to 1 a.m., was the 
result of a monthlong investigation by the department's narcotics and vice 
unit. ORANGE COUNTY 
</P>
