<HEADLINE>
<P>
'94 FOOTBALL PREVIEW; CITY SECTION; SOUTHERN PACIFIC CONFERENCE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Crenshaw 
</P>
<P>
 COACH: Robert Garrett, 7th year. 
</P>
